This issue was previously identified and reported to be fixed [here]( https://github.com/grafana/grafana/issues/115027)

However I'm still seeing this as an issue on Grafana Cloud


<img width="2499" height="797" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/4280128a-1d6c-4f18-ad25-12fb50c1e5d2" />


