### What happened?

The snowflake datasource is returning all numbers as strings even tho the query is clearly returning numbers. This effects visualizing anything as timeseries etc.

[reproduced here](https://datasourcedev.grafana-dev.net/d/tidwj4v/snowflake?orgId=1&from=now-6h&to=now&timezone=browser&editPanel=1)

```
SELECT  
  TO_NUMBER(1) AS value
```

